title: Fozzy at puppy playtime
description:
Here's our Fozzy at 20 weeks in his puppy playtime group at the local Petco! Fozzy is the cream-colored husky mix with the red-and-black harness.

I created this video with the YouTube Video Editor (http://www.youtube.com/editor)
